OL,3,CHit-and-run victim makes appeal from
OL,4,Chospital bed
OL,6,FLiz Pullen said "I ended up in the
OL,7,Fgutter on the other side of the road,
OL,8,Fwith the bike on the floor and me on
OL,9,Fthe floor in pain. It's just
OL,10,Fdevastating. I can't do anything much
OL,11,Ffor myself. I have to rely on people
OL,12,Fto help me with basic every day things
OL,13,Flike washing and going to the
OL,14,Fbathroom."
