OL,3,CHit-and-run victim makes appeal from
OL,4,Chospital bed
OL,6,FLiz's wife Julie says it makes her
OL,7,Ffeel sick seeing the road where the
OL,8,Fincident happened. "I got a call about
OL,9,F5:30 pm so I drove down as safely as I
OL,10,Fcould, to find Liz in a pile on the
OL,11,Ffloor. Lots of people were helping,
OL,12,Fwith lots of coats over her. The
OL,13,Fpolice had arrived by then. I was
OL,14,Ftold, basically it was a hit-and-run."
OL,16,FLiz's favourite pastime is Walking and
OL,17,Fshe's taken part in several charity
OL,18,Fwalks. However she says such
OL,19,Fendeavours seem a world away at
OL,20,Fpresent.
