OL,6,FThe collision involved a white flatbed
OL,7,Fvan. And she's sent this appeal to the
OL,8,Fdriver. "I'd like to think you have
OL,9,Fsome kind of conscience and would
OL,10,Fnever have wanted anything like this
OL,11,Fto have happened to somebody. Please,
OL,12,Fplease come forward."
OL,14,FHampshire Police have released this
OL,15,FAppeal:
