OL,3,CHit-and-run victim makes appeal from
OL,4,Chospital bed
OL,6,FWe are appealing for witnesses and
OL,7,Fdash cam footage following a fail-to-
OL,8,Fstop collision in Portsmouth. Police
OL,9,Fwere called by the ambulance service
OL,10,Fat 5.22pm on Friday 23 January to a
OL,11,Freport of a road traffic collision on
OL,12,FBurrfields Road. This involved a blue
OL,13,Fmotorcycle and a white van. The
OL,14,Fmotorcyclist, a woman in her 50s,
OL,15,Fsuffered serious leg injuries but the
OL,16,Fdriver of the van did not stop at the
OL,17,Fscene.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/6
